{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"Crypto","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/API/Crypto","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Crypto_API\">Web Crypto API <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Crypto\"><code>Crypto</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Eigenschaften</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Crypto/subtle\"><code>subtle</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methoden</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Crypto/getRandomValues\"><code>getRandomValues()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Crypto/randomUUID\"><code>randomUUID()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Ähnliche Seiten zu Web Crypto API</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CryptoKey\"><code>CryptoKey</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SubtleCrypto\"><code>SubtleCrypto</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/crypto_property\"><code>crypto_property</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>Die&nbsp;<code><strong>Crypto</strong></code>-Schnittstelle bietet grundlegende kryptographische Funktionen, die im aktuellen Kontext verfügbar sind. Sie ermöglicht den Zugriff auf kryptographische Primitive wie z.B. einen&nbsp;verschlüsselungstechnisch starken Zufallszahlengenerator.</p>\n\n<p>Ein Objekt mit dieser Schnittstelle ist im Web-Kontext über die Eigenschaft <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/crypto_property\"><code>Window.crypto</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> verfügbar.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"eigenschaften","title":"Eigenschaften","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>Diese Schnittstelle implementiert Eigenschaften, die unter <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Crypto/getRandomValues\"><code>RandomSource</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> definiert sind.</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"crypto.subtle_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Crypto/subtle\"><code>Crypto.subtle</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></dt>\n <dd>Gibt ein <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SubtleCrypto\"><code>SubtleCrypto</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>-Objekt zurück, das Zugriff auf einfache kryptographische Methoden wie Hash-Funktionen, Signierung, Ver- und Entschlüsselung ermöglicht.</dd>\n <dt id=\"sect1\">&nbsp;</dt>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methoden","title":"Methoden","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>Diese Schnittstelle implementiert Methoden, die unter&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Crypto/getRandomValues\"><code>RandomSource</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> beschrieben sind.</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"crypto.getrandomvalues_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Crypto/getRandomValues\"><code>Crypto.getRandomValues()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Füllt das übergebene <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"Die Beschreibung hierüber wurde bisher noch nicht geschrieben. Bitte überlege, mitzuwirken!\"><code>TypedArray</code></a> mit kryptographisch sinnvollen Zufallswerten.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Spezifikation</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Kommentar</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/WebCryptoAPI/#crypto-interface\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web Cryptography API<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'Crypto' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Empfehlung</span></td>\n   <td>Ursprüngliche Definition</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser-Kompatibilität","id":"browser-kompatibilität","isH3":false,"query":"api.Crypto","dataURL":"/de/docs/Web/API/Crypto/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect2\">\n\n\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Components.utils.importGlobalProperties\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">Components.utils.importGlobalProperties</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Eigenschaften","id":"eigenschaften"},{"text":"Methoden","id":"methoden"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"},{"text":"Browser-Kompatibilität","id":"browser-kompatibilität"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"}],"summary":"Die Crypto-Schnittstelle bietet grundlegende kryptographische Funktionen, die im aktuellen Kontext verfügbar sind. Sie ermöglicht den Zugriff auf kryptographische Primitive wie z.B. einen verschlüsselungstechnisch starken Zufallszahlengenerator.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Crypto","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Crypto","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Crypto","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Crypto","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Crypto","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Crypto","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Crypto","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Crypto","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/crypto","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/crypto/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Crypto","title":"Crypto"}],"pageTitle":"Crypto - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}